        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 13 at 3:51PM MDT until July 13 at 4:30PM MDT by NWS El Paso Tx/Santa Teresa NM</headline>
        <description>SVREPZ

The National Weather Service in El Paso has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northwestern Hudspeth County in western Texas...
Northeastern El Paso County in western Texas...

* Until 430 PM MDT.

* At 351 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Hueco Tanks,
and is nearly stationary.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage
to roofs, siding, and trees.

* Locations impacted include...
Loma Linda, Desert Haven, Hueco Tanks, Hueco Mountain Estates,
Butterfield, and Homestead Meadows.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
